=== Sound Staff ===

'''Yukihide Takekawa''' (竹川幸秀) composed the entire Soul Blazer soundtrack. He was a member of the Japanese rock band "The Alfee" and brought a distinctive melodic style to the game's music.

Notable tracks:
* '''Main Theme''' - Orchestral opening
* '''World of Evil''' - Haunting dungeon theme
* '''GreenWood''' - Pastoral town music
* '''Leo's House''' - Emotional character theme
* '''Dr. Leo's Lab''' - Scientific, mechanical
* '''Final Battle''' - Epic boss confrontation

